{"tid":1289710,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實 林靜怡箍牙好唔好","createTime":"2019-07-06T08:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T06:01:04.000Z","uid":106481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7438619263e4a8087a8ded07d93bfc9356b64e3","tid":1289710,"uid":106481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:20:51.000Z","msg":"我consult完覺得佢做啲配套幾好咁<br />\n但有人話佢收左錢就唔係果回事<br />\n網上好似好多打手&hellip;<br />\n求箍過嘅巴打絲打俾啲真實comment 感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b3190f1c110e2a4d13d2240dae464dcf4a19fd","tid":1289710,"uid":114032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢間ok<br />\n本來要箍一年隱適美，不過因為有排戴得唔夠耐，<br />\n搞到前前後後&gt;一年半先箍完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總共見過林靜怡4次左右，<br />\n負責consult同檢查下箍牙嘅進度<br />\n佢有樣野好嘅就係我本來有智慧齒打橫生，<br />\n問過佢駛唔駛剝咗先箍，佢話無乜影響<br />\n都算係唔hard sell，比著出面實係咁谷我剝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落手整嘅多數係其他牙醫，手勢同態度都唔錯<br />\n如果你返工又想戴隱適美嘅要有心理準備請半日假睇牙<br />\n<br />\n隱適美覆診比較密，同埋喺診所成日等好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好搵多幾間比較，<br />\n特別係如果你個情況比較複雜<br />\n我個人都係覺得鋼箍效果好啲，但怕麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906dd8dead10043a513fdc6ae0861880423ad59d","tid":1289710,"uid":206613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"可唔可以了解下箍咗幾錢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142e7010966cabd57664c9fc3b43be16ec2b1d31","tid":1289710,"uid":106481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1b3190f1c110e2a4d13d2240dae464dcf4a19fd","tid":1289710,"uid":114032,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T09:08:07.000Z","msg":"我覺得呢間ok<br />\n本來要